  "instructions": [
    "preheat a comal or griddle to 375\u000359f",
    "knead the rye bread and flour mixture to combine",
    "shape the dough into a flat circle, about 1/4 inch thick",
    "brush with olive oil and sprinkle with salt",
    "heat the comal or griddle for 2-3 minutes, until hot",
    "place the dough on the comal or griddle and cook for 2-3 minutes, until crispy and golden",
    "flip the dough over and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until crispy and golden",
    "remove from heat and let cool for 2-3 minutes",
    "sprinkle with feta cheese, fresh oregano, and lemon juice",
    "serve warm and enjoy",
    "crumble the feta cheese and sprinkle on top of the flatbread"
